@NODE Intro "bSP mARKER - eXTERNAL fILE mARKING fOR mAXS bBS aND mAGIC FILE 3.x"
----------[ ˇNTRODUCTION ]--------------------------------------------------

BSP Marker is an external file marking system for Maxs BBS and Magic File
3.x.  This file needs a version of Magic File ( by Steve Clack ) greater
then or equal to version 3 in order to function properly.

                  oN aMINET: comm/maxs/MagicFilexx.lha

                where xx is a version number, ie, 35 (3.5)

BSP Marker allows you to mark files for a user of your BBS, while he or she
is either online, in the BBS, or offline.  My two main uses for this program
are to mark files which people have mailed me for, asking for me to mark a
file ready for automatic download, or while chatting to the user, so the
user can just hit [D] to grab the file :)

I certainly have a use for this program, and I hope other people may be able
to use it to it's full advantage as well.

@{"  Back to main menu...  " link MAIN}
@ENDNODE

